reviewText: I've had a copy of this video for years, but it got ruined a long time ago and figured it's about time for a new one for replace the other one. This video sure shows plenty of knowledge on Deer hunting tips and strategies to help you be more successful! It even has an all-star cast of expert hunters such as wildlife biologist Dr. Grant Woods, Will Primos of Primos Hunting Calls, Harold Knight and David Hale of Knight & Hale Game Calls, along with the late Dick Kirby of Quaker Boy Game Calls. This video will help you become a better Deer hunter.
